r Group with Vocal Let's Go Crazy, Take Me With U, The Beautiful Ones, Computer Blue, Darling Nikki, When Doves Cry, I Would Die 4 U, Baby I'm a Star, Purple Rain Beastie Boys License to Ill 1986 Mercury Records noawardsbutthistablecelliswide Rhymin &amp; Stealin, The New Style, She's Crafty, Posse in Effect, Slow Ride, Girls, (You Gotta) Fight for Your Right, No Sleep Till Brooklyn, Paul Revere, Hold It Now, Hit It, Brass Monkey, Slow and Low, Time to Get Ill <p>Code snippets like <code>var foo = "bar";</code> can be shown inline.</p> <p>Also, <code>this should vertically align</code> ~~<code>with this</code>~~ ~~and this~~.</p> <p>Code can also be shown in a block element.</p> <pre><code>var foo = "bar";
